title: Janis Joplin In Frankfurt 1969-04-12
description:
Another gem from the bootleg archive.

Please enjoy, share and seed :)


Janis Joplin Live In Frankfurt 1969-04-12 German Documentary with astounding video footage! NTSC DVD

This documentary consists of remembrances, a London interview overdubbed in German, plus some right-in-your-face color film footage from the Frankfurt Festhalle in great quality.

I've added chapters and menu, as there were only VOB files when I received this.

Enjoy!

A DoinkerTape
